        <h2>What MyTaxCalcs Is Not</h2>
        <p>MyTaxCalcs does not provide tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice. We are not a CPA firm, a tax preparation service, or a licensed financial advisor. The calculators on this site are educational tools for estimation purposes. Every taxpayer's situation is different — always consult a qualified professional for advice specific to your circumstances.</p>

